flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Ask user for topic]
    B --> C[Build prompt with topic<br/>and rejected jokes]
    C --> D[Call LLM to generate joke]
    D --> E[Display joke to user]
    E --> F{User approves?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Accept joke]
    F -->|No| H[Record rejected joke]
    H --> C
    G --> I([End])